  <brief_title>Effect of Composition and Timing of Ingestion of Fluids on the Urinary Excretion of Lithogenic Substances</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Composition and Timing of Ingestion of Fluids on the Urinary Excretion of Lithogenic Substances</official_title>
