  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Interventional crossover study on healthy volunteers aimed at evaluating the effect of the
      composition and timing of ingestion of different types of water on the urinary excretion of
      lithogenic substances; the study will also analyze the effect of potassium citrate on urine
      pH and lithogenic substances
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
